<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Redemption Request</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .alert-message {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .alert-message h2 {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .alert-message p {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .request-details {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
            border: 2px solid #FF9933;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .request-details h3 {
            color: #138808;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .details-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 250px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FF9933;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding: 8px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .urgent-notice {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .urgent-notice p {
            color: #155724;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-approve {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-reject {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #fd7e14 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .details-grid {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Indians in Ghana</h1>
            <p>Merchant Portal</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="alert-message">
                <h2>üé´ New Redemption Request</h2>
                <p>A customer wants to redeem one of your deals</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="request-details">
                <h3>Redemption Request Details</h3>
                
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Customer Name</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{customerName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Deal Title</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{dealTitle}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Request Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{requestDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="urgent-notice">
                <p><strong>‚è∞ Action Required:</strong> Please review and respond to this redemption request promptly. Customers appreciate quick responses!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>How to respond:</strong></p>
                <ol style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Click on "Approve Request" if the customer can redeem the deal</li>
                    <li>Click on "Reject Request" if there are any issues</li>
                    <li>You can also manage requests from your merchant dashboard</li>
                    <li>Customers will be notified of your decision automatically</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: cards@indiansinghana.com | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                <p>{{businessName}}</p>
                <p>This email was sent to {{merchantEmail}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
